author: 13abc
title: Win an all expense paid vacation and help local cancer patients
text:
Related Links The Victory Center TOLEDO (13abc Action News) - The Victory Center provides free support and programs to hundreds of cancer patients, survivors and their families every year. You have a chance to help the organization do all that good work and take a fabulous trip!
The Victory Center is raffling off an all expense paid trip for two to Cancun, Mexico. Tickets are $20 dollars each and the raffle runs through the end of the month. Dianne Cherry is the Executive Director, "We provide everything from oncology massage to facials, yoga and other exercise classes. Facials, aquatic therapy, support groups and the list goes on and on. And it's all free? Everything we do here at the victory center is free for cancer patients, survivors and their families."
Tickets will be sold through Halloween and the drawing is November 2. You can buy tickets at The Victory Center or online.
